title: Site Reliability Engineer
description: Looking for an experienced SRE to maintain and improve our cloud infrastructure. Will be responsible for implementing monitoring solutions, automating deployment processes, and ensuring system reliability. Must have strong experience with AWS, Docker, and CI/CD pipelines.
notes: Need someone who can start ASAP. Previous candidates lacked Docker expertise.

title: Frontend Developer
description: Frontend developer needed for educational platform development. Must be proficient in JavaScript and modern frameworks. Experience with responsive design and accessibility requirements is essential.

title: Data Scientist
description: Seeking a Data Scientist with strong ML expertise to join our biotech analytics team. Will develop predictive models and analyze large datasets. Must have experience with Python, AI/ML frameworks, and statistical analysis.
notes: PhD preferred but not required if extensive industry experience.

title: Security Engineer
description: Security engineers needed for implementing robust security measures across cloud infrastructure. Experience with AWS security, penetration testing, and security compliance required. Will work on security automation and incident response.

title: Software Architect
description: Looking for a Software Architect to lead technical design and implementation of educational software solutions. Will oversee architectural decisions and mentor development teams. Strong background in Java, Spring, and cloud technologies required.

title: Backend Developer
description: Backend developers needed for API development and database optimization. Must be proficient in PHP, Laravel, and PostgreSQL. Experience with RESTful APIs and microservices architecture required.
notes: Remote work possible for the right candidates.

title: Scrum Master
description: Experienced Scrum Master needed to facilitate agile processes and remove impediments for multiple development teams. Must have CSM certification and experience with scaling agile frameworks.

title: QA Engineer
description: QA Engineers needed for automated testing implementation. Experience with test automation frameworks and CI/CD tools required. Will develop and maintain test suites for educational software platforms.
notes: Strong JavaScript and Python skills preferred.

title: Business Analyst
description: Seeking a Business Analyst to bridge the gap between business needs and technical solutions. Will gather requirements, create documentation, and work closely with development teams. Healthcare industry experience preferred.

title: Cloud Engineer
description: Cloud Engineers needed for infrastructure modernization project. Strong experience with AWS and Google Cloud required. Will implement IaC and manage cloud resources across multiple environments.

title: Machine Learning Engineer
description: Looking for an experienced Machine Learning Engineer to develop and implement advanced ML models and algorithms. Will be responsible for building scalable ML pipelines and working with large datasets to drive business insights. Must have strong experience with Python, Spark, and AWS ML services.
notes: Priority role for Q4 healthcare analytics project.

title: Solutions Architect
description: Seeking a Solutions Architect to design and implement cloud-native applications. Will lead technical discussions with clients and provide architectural guidance to development teams. Must have extensive experience with AWS, Azure, and microservices architecture.

title: UX Designer
description: Looking for creative UX Designers to join our growing product team. Will be responsible for creating user-centered designs, conducting user research, and developing interactive prototypes. Experience with educational technology products and design systems required.
notes: Expanding design team for new product launch.

title: Database Administrator
description: Seeking an experienced DBA to manage and optimize our database infrastructure. Responsibilities include performance tuning, backup and recovery, and security implementation. Strong expertise in Oracle and MySQL required.

title: Full Stack Developer
description: Seeking Full Stack Developers with strong experience in Node.js, Vue.js, and MongoDB. Will be responsible for developing and maintaining healthcare analytics applications. Must have experience with RESTful APIs and modern development practices.
